title: 'Nice quality pencils'
body: The pencils look glamorous. Thanks to its fully black body even the inner woods. This feels premium. Pencils are very slim and it feels like they will be broken if I give pressure on them, but that's not the case. Leads are quite dark but certainly can not be put into the extra dark category. I think DOMS Fusion much darker pencil. Pentonic pencils are much darker with a premium and elegant look. However, Stallion has its own charm with its full blackness. A good purchase indeed
